tigase.component.modules

Class AbstractModule<CTX extends Context>

  • java.lang.Object
    • tigase.component.modules.AbstractModule<CTX>
  • Type Parameters:
    CTX - context of component.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContextAware, InitializingModule, Module
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractEventBusModule, AdHocCommandModule, DiscoveryModule, JabberVersionModule, XmppPingModule

    public abstract class AbstractModule<CTX extends Context>
extends Object
implements Module, ContextAware, InitializingModule
    Abstract class for help building a module. It has implemented few default methods from Module, ContextAware and InitializingModule.
    Author:
    bmalkow
